                "podcastId": 28,
                "author": "Rocketship LLC",
                "description": "Part two of our mini-series on Jobs To Be Done today. We welcome back Bob Moesta who spent hours with us recording real interviews with Industry attendees and unpacking the conversations to answer the question - what Job does Industry serve for it&rsquo;s attendees.\nToday, we get to hear one of those interviews as Bob shows us some of the essential techniques of Jobs To Be Done interviews.&nbsp;\nAdding&nbsp;Jobs to be Done&nbsp;to your bag of tricks gives you a leg up in the product world. We breakdown Bob Moesta&rsquo;s exclusive interviews with actual customers of Industry conference. The best way to learn is by unpacking real decisions that consumers have actually made and this is a rare opportunity to learn from the master himself.",
